            <h2>About spider-man</h2>
            <p>
            Spider-Man, also known as Peter Parker, is one of the most iconic superheroes in the world. 
            He gained his powers after being bitten by a <a href="https://bwscience.com/where-can-you-find-a-radioactive-spider/">radioactive spider</a>, which gave him <a href="https://www.looper.com/771880/all-of-spider-mans-powers-explained/">abilities</a> 
            like wall-climbing, super strength, agility, and spider-sense.
        </p>

        <p>
            He protects New York City from dangerous villains while balancing his personal life. 
            His journey is guided by the famous quote, "With great power comes great responsibility."
        </p>
